long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Type Genius is powered by GPT, a state-of-the-art natural language processing AI developed by OpenAI. This groundbreaking Chrome extension elevates your browsing experience by providing suggestions to complete your text in textareas across web pages. Now, you can enjoy fast, intelligent, and context-aware autocomplete suggestions for your searches, emails, social media posts, and more!
